{"tid":2127361,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[真人真事]如何喺放飯時間去郊野公園食晏","createTime":"2020-07-27T09:31:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T14:38:06.000Z","uid":229020,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cfe45c8e674909f1f50f54337e7427919f216ff0","tid":2127361,"uid":229020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:31:11.000Z","msg":"是咁的，原本我係一個中環打工仔，人工唔算高20K，獨力照顧家中老母親<br />\n起初政府禁止堂食，我係支持的，反正平時喺公司食外賣九秒九食完又開工 ,對我根本無影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係仆街老細因為公司有一半人HomeOffice竟然為咗開源節流，晏晝唔開冷氣，眾所鳩知 *公司* 冇開冷氣係熱過郊野公園<br />\n大部分同事寧願唔食飯喺商場嘆冷氣，但係我唔同，我唔食我個30kg肚腩都要食，咁我唯有一放飯即刻搽防曬，直接衝上薄扶林郊野公園，途中用電話叫foodpanda，天真嘅我以為喺一個鐘頭之內食完個外賣可以再即刻衝返公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知仆街foodpanda契弟遲到，搞到我都遲返公司，老細叫我聽日唔使返工了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔講啦啱啱收到order，又要送去薄扶林郊野公園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e584bcb76c4b0b26a6a6495e9d87f14f04c850c","tid":2127361,"uid":229020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:32:10.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"c8e99a02067b97bc48d1c6b201f4e55035c9e95d","tid":2127361,"uid":229020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:39:08.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"4a112acc40a92354111eaac8f19bca4c919588da","tid":2127361,"uid":177955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:39:09.000Z","msg":"sorry吖契爺 嗰次無心㗎<br />\n大人有大量唔好同小弟爭飯食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n家有兩老等住養<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e852afc4d665c5d44af7f7ed00234a166f8c09","tid":2127361,"uid":138479,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:39:18.000Z","msg":"冇「是咁的」，0分重作"},{"pid":"f903a3b0b0a0b7fe7c1bb0ced6569f8a4d149e98","tid":2127361,"uid":229020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2e852afc4d665c5d44af7f7ed00234a166f8c09","tid":2127361,"uid":138479,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:39:18.000Z","msg":"冇「是咁的」，0分重作"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:40:36.000Z","msg":"頭三隻字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c444bebaebd587c9c870a48b957d2950e713dab","tid":2127361,"uid":177955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:42:16.000Z","msg":"樓主啊 求你啦"},{"pid":"ff1db68ff10b80d868ffb78c28dfc5042ecc9d80","tid":2127361,"uid":177955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:43:13.000Z","msg":"自從嗰次之後,我啲單少咗好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d50eb6c37cc2dd6f3f3f6be56d234b34b12fe49","tid":2127361,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:52:58.000Z","msg":"個foodpanda 心諗邊個係山上面叫外賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"595cf297272fde21c86c3d88b7ffac61ff2e8891","tid":2127361,"uid":229020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:20:03.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"b33806750339b0f999a38882d193826a5ed5f3da","tid":2127361,"uid":71635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d50eb6c37cc2dd6f3f3f6be56d234b34b12fe49","tid":2127361,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:52:58.000Z","msg":"個foodpanda 心諗邊個係山上面叫外賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:21:55.000Z","msg":"最後張單玩野唔送就食西北風<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"addaf8342eaa7d04fed737747ffd987d93002145","tid":2127361,"uid":318825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:24:19.000Z","msg":"大肚婆去冇律敦治<br />\n扣分"},{"pid":"e6b7c1d691a1c2ac0ad4e4fa37fc0f712160f4f3","tid":2127361,"uid":229020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:15:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.